content: I want you to do that, and I want you to get in, just redo all the data that's in there, and put in sample data that you feel doesn't have to be a lot, just enough that you need to test. And put it in there, and let me check it. Let me see if you need to get better some places, and let me see the sample data, and see if we're really on the same page with everything. And if we are, great, we can move forward. If we're not, we'll figure it out quick. But I think testing and data integrity are extremely important, and we have to have those principles. We have to have data integrity.
